{"metadata":{"role":"sampleCode","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"title":"Managing Mobile Devices","roleHeading":"WWDC10"},"abstract":[{"text":"Devices running iPhone OS are as easy to configure and manage as they are to use. Learn about the new Mobile Device Management architecture and discover how to use new Over-The-Air (OTA) capabilities to erase or lock a device and query for important device information. OTA also lets you remotely deploy configuration profiles, install in-house applications, and make managed iPhone deployments even more manageable.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc10-108-managing-mobile-devices"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"article","sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2010\/108\/","overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex"}},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10-108-Managing-Mobile-Devices","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10"]]},"references":{"WWDC10.jpeg":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10.jpeg"}],"type":"image","identifier":"WWDC10.jpeg","alt":null},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{"